        <mxCell id="stage1-desc" value="• Read {task_id}_plan.json&#xa;• Auto-detect task_type from&#xa;  keywords (fix → bugfix,&#xa;  upgrade → upgrade, refactor)&#xa;• Resolve file_path from&#xa;  architecture_facts.json&#xa;  (ID match → name fallback)&#xa;• Select Strategy class" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=9;" vertex="1" parent="1">
